    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Medium-influence, High-consequence COU at MRL 2. Validation evidence from PIV comparison and bench hemolysis measurements, supplemented by consolidated literature evidence for model form selection, supports the claim that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all 5 operating points with adequate validation uncertainty margin.",
